海是指地球上与[[洋|洋]]相互连接的水域系统，包括[[國際海道測量組織|國際海道測量組織]]命名的四个大洋<ref name=ihorg>[[國際海道測量組織|International Hydrographic Organization]]（IHO）. "[http://www.iho-ohi.net/iho_pubs/standard/S-23/S23_1953.pdf Limits of Oceans and Seas (Special Publication №28)] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008191433/http://www.iho-ohi.net/iho_pubs/standard/S-23/S23_1953.pdf |date=2011-10-08 }}", 3rd ed. Imp. Monégasque ([[Monte_Carlo|Monte Carlo]]), 1953. Retrieved 7 February 2010.</ref>——[[大西洋|大西洋]]、[[太平洋|太平洋]]、[[印度洋|印度洋]]、[[北冰洋|北冰洋]]—和[[南冰洋|南冰洋]]及其所包含的水域<ref name="oed">''[[牛津英語詞典|Oxford English Dictionary]]'', {{nowrap|1st ed.}} "sea, ''n.''" Oxford University Press (Oxford), 1911.</ref>。

縱然海比較細小（除了[[北大西洋環流|北大西洋環流]]產生的[[马尾藻海|马尾藻海]]是個值得注意的例外<ref name=Stow/>{{rp|page=90}}），而且通常被比大陸為細小的陸地圍繞<ref name="oceanservice.noaa">National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration. [http://oceanservice.noaa.gov/facts/oceanorsea.html "What's the Difference between an Ocean and a Sea?"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119004542/http://oceanservice.noaa.gov/facts/oceanorsea.html |date=2017-01-19 }} in ''Ocean Facts''.</ref>。海一般比[[湖泊|湖泊]]大，盛載[[海水|海水]]<ref name="Nishri">{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1016/S0009-2541(99)00007-8| title = Lake Kinneret (The Sea of Galilee): The effects of diversion of external salinity sources and the probable chemical composition of the internal salinity sources| journal = Chemical Geology| volume = 158| pages = 37–52| year = 1999| last1 = Nishri | first1 = A. | last2 = Stiller | first2 = M. | last3 = Rimmer | first3 = A. | last4 = Geifman | first4 = Y. | last5 = Krom | first5 = M. }}</ref>。海洋學家對海還沒有已被接納的技術性定義{{efn|一种定义视海为海洋的分支，尽管现在[[國際海道測量組織|國際海道測量組織]]以一种被视为合乎习俗但相当主观的方式<ref>American Society of Civil Engineers (1994). [https://books.google.com/books?id=jPVxSDzVRP0C&pg=PA365 ''The Glossary of the Mapping Sciences''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=jPVxSDzVRP0C&pg=PA365 |date=20210417212011 }}. p. 365. ASCE Publications. ISBN 0-7844-7570-9.</ref> 将世界上海洋的边界按照没有被另外包括于海中的海域来定义<ref name=ihorg/>。另一种说法认为“海”是对于一个大部分被陆地包围的水体的简称<ref>Karleskint, George (2009). [https://books.google.com/?id=0JkKOFIj5pgC&pg=PA47 ''Introduction to Marine Biology'']. p. 47. Cengage Learning. ISBN 978-0-495-56197-2.</ref>，这种说法就没有包括[[马尾藻海|马尾藻海]]的情况。第三种理论认为海以[[#Basin|海盆]]为底，这种说法包含了[[裏海|里海]]的情形，因为里海曾经是古代一片海洋的一部分。<ref>Conforti, B. (2005). [https://books.google.com/?id=tLcin2NyJQgC&pg=PA237 ''The Italian Yearbook of International Law'']. Vol. 14, p. 237. Martinus Nijhoff. ISBN 978-90-04-15027-0.</ref>}}。在[[国际法|国际法]]中《[[聯合國海洋法公約|聯合國海洋法公約]]》列明所有海洋也屬於「海」<ref>Vukas, B. (2004) [https://books.google.com/books?id=sbqBvQy04XwC&pg=PA271 ''The Law of the Sea: Selected Writings''] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sbqBvQy04XwC&pg=PA271 |date=20210325011551 }}. p. 271. Martinus Nijhoff. ISBN 978-90-04-13863-6.</ref>{{efn|相应地，这一公约并不适用于[[裏海|里海]]的情况，在[[国际法|法律]]角度中它被视为“国际湖泊”。<ref>{{cite journal | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=uxmInSrE9vQC&pg=PA74 | title = The Politics of Caspian Oil | isbn = 978-0-333-73973-0 | author1 = Gokay | first1 = Bulent | date = 2001 | page = 74 | publisher = Palgrave Macmillan | journal =  | access-date = 2017-01-03 | archive-date = 2021-03-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210325011539/https://books.google.com/books?id=uxmInSrE9vQC&pg=PA74 | dead-url = no }}</ref>}}。

另外，世界各地也存在很多湖泊被以“海”来命名，如[[里海|里海]]、[[加利利海|加利利海]]<ref name="Nishri"/>、[[死海|死海]]、[[什刹海|什刹海]]、[[洱海|洱海]]、[[邛海|邛海]]等等。

